<v-app>
  <Navbar :laps="laps" />

  <v-content>
    <Timer
      :timer="formattedTime"
      :state="timerState"
      @start="start"
      @lap="lap"
      @pause="pause"
      @stop="stop"
    />
  </v-content>

  <v-snackbar
    v-model="snackbar"
    color="info"
    :timeout="2000"
  >
    New Lap {{ this.latestLap }}
    <v-btn dark flat @click="snackbar = false">Close</v-btn>
  </v-snackbar>
</v-app>
